# Pointer Explanation
* Pointer i (red): everything before it needs to be a 0; aka beginning of 1's
* Pointer j (blue): needs to always point to a 1 (the "iterating" pointer)
* Pointer k (green): everything after it needs to be a 2; aka end of 1's

