solutions.content:
**Approach is simple:**

if current element= 0 send it to left
or
if  current element=2 send it to right, 
or
if  current element=1 then do nothing(skip current element).

```
class Solution {

public static void sortColors(int[] arr) {
int l=0;
int m=0; 
int h=arr.length-1;
while(m<=h)
{
    if(arr[m]==0){ //element is 0
        swap(arr,l,m);
        l++;
        m++;
    } else if(arr[m]==2){
        swap(arr,m,h);
        h--;
    }
    else m++;
}
  }

 private static void swap(int[] array, int i, int j) {
    int temp = array[i];
    array[i] = array[j];
    array[j] = temp;
  }
}
```

